### Subscriptions Service Requests

@host = http://localhost:8080
@token = <paste access token>
@internalKey = dev-change-me

### Check access for current user
GET {{host}}/api/v1/subscriptions/me/has-access
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get active subscription for current user
GET {{host}}/api/v1/subscriptions/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Activate subscription (internal)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/internal/subscriptions/activate
X-INTERNAL-KEY: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "<uuid>",
  "plan": "PRO",
  "durationDays": 30,
  "txId": "optional-tx"
}

### Cancel subscription (internal)
POST {{host}}/api/v1/internal/subscriptions/cancel
X-INTERNAL-KEY: {{internalKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "<uuid>",
  "reason": "User requested cancellation"
}
